content: As an AI language model, I cannot guarantee the effectiveness of home remedies for under eye bags, and as for how long it takes to see results, it varies from person to person. Some people may see results immediately while others may take a few days or even a week to notice a difference. Plus, the severity of the bags may also play a role in how long it takes to see results. However, consistently practicing these remedies and making lifestyle changes could help with under-eye bags in the long term. If the issue persists, it is important to consult a doctor or dermatologist.
